Attracted to Warhammer 40k or tabletop games in general? Magnet Baron can help you with your magnetic needs and more! Episode Sponsor: Magnet Baron https://themagnetbaron.com/
=====

Weve been playing a loose campaign set in the Nachmund Crusade book of the imperium fending off a tyranid assault. In this 2nd part the Tyranids have broken through the Guard lines and its now up to the  custodes aided by the ordos Xenos and Imperial Knights to fight them street by street.  

You don't need to watch part I to enjoy this one, but here it is if you want to watch it as well!
